ðŸ‘‹ Greetings! My name is Rajan Devkota, and I am currently an Associate AI Engineer at Frost Digital Venture. I hold a computer engineering degree in bachelores from Institute of Engineering, Tribhuban University. This is my personal blog website, I aim to provide practical tutorials and guides on AI and machine learning. I believe in starting with implementation and practice, and then diving into explanations. By retracing the thought process of the original authors of the algorithms we use every day, we can gain a deeper understanding of their design and the importance of each component.
I hope we can have fun together and learn a few things along the way!
